A notice is pinned to the board, stamped with the royal seal of Gondor:

'A brave adventurer is needed to claim territory in Agarnaith!

A camp of Uruk-hai guards the pass around Mount Doom and the road into Agarnaith. This overlook has strategic significance to The Conquest of Mordor. We request that an adventurer go and remove any enemies fortified there, and take the land in the name of Gondor.'
